            "value": "<i>Graphics reporter Elizabeth Commisso can be contacted at </i><a href=\"mailto:elizabeth.commisso@columbiaspectator.com\"><i>elizabeth.commisso@columbiaspectator.com</i></a><i>. Follow Spectator on Twitter at </i><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ColumbiaSpec?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor\"><i>@ColumbiaSpec</i></a><i>.</i>"
          }
        ],
        "headline": "As COVID-19 cases rise, so does food insecurity among the homeless. Can food providers and shelters keep up?",
